Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:06.56,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,February 7th. Interview for testimony from a witness to the suicide of a high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:12.54,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,Before we begin questioning, I’d like to confirm your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:15.52,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,Shinji Makino, 29 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:18.57,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,Office worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:20.98,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:23.56,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,Could you state your address?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:30.16,Default,Shinji,0,0,0,,Sure. Shinagawa ward, Kamiosaki, 30-19-105, Meguro-residence 504.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:31.96,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:37.12,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,This interview will be recorded, by the way, but it will be kept confidential, so please don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:38.13,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:39.56,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,Let’s get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:43.26,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,Could you tell me what you saw at the scene of the suicide in as much detail as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:48.37,Default,Shinji,0,0,0,,Where do you want me to start? From the morning of that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:52.42,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,No. Just what you remember from around the time of the suicide. Relax. Don’t feel pressured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:54.16,Default,Shinji,0,0,0,,Uhh.
